   244Ôćĺ### `[output.html.search]` ÔÇŽ
   286Ôćĺ#### `[output.html.search.chapter]`
   288ÔćĺThe [`output.html.search.chapter`] table provides the ability to modify search settings per chapter or directory. Each key is the path to the chapter source file or directory, and the value is a table of settings to apply to that path. This will merge recursively, with more specific paths taking precedence.
   289Ôćĺ
   290Ôćĺ```toml
   291Ôćĺ[output.html.search.chapter]
   292Ôćĺ# Disables search indexing for all chapters in the `appendix` directory.
   293Ôćĺ"appendix" = { enable = false }
   294Ôćĺ# Enables search indexing for just this one appendix chapter.
   295Ôćĺ"appendix/glossary.md" = { enable = true }
   296Ôćĺ```
   297Ôćĺ
      ÔćĺÔÇŽ
   300Ôćĺ### `[output.html.redirect]` ÔÇŽ
   325Ôćĺ## Markdown renderer ÔÇŽ
